public class Row
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.cloudata.core.common.io.CWritable, java.lang.Comparable<Row>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable

Row is Value Object which represents Table's row.
A Row object has multiple columns.
Each column has multiple Cell Objects
